Privacy

To see how many visitors use the site, this website uses Matomo (formerly known as PIWIK), an analytics tool. It uses cookies. No data is submitted to third parties because Matomo is hosted on our own server, and all IP addresses are anonymized. You can choose not to be tracked any time by activating the Do-not-track function in your Browser settings, or by opt-ing out using the form below (if you already have do-not-track activated, it will only display a notice):
